Calypso is a simulation programs for MHD dynamo simulation in a rotating spherical shell using spherical harmonics expansion methods.
Calypso consists of the following files and directories.

% ls
CMakeLists.txt    Makefile.in    configure       doxygen           work
INSTALL           README         configure.in    examples
LICENSE           bin            doc             src

INSTALL: Brief installation procedure
LICENSE: License
README:  This file

configure.in:     Input file for autoconf
Makefile.in:      Template for Makefile used by configure
configure:        Configuration script
CMakeLists.txt:   Configuration file for CMake

bin:      Directory for programs
doc:      Direcory for documentation
doxygen:  Directory for Source documentation 
examples: Directory for examples
src:      Directory for source files
work:     Work directory


For installation, prease read document in doc directory or INSTALL.
